org.joda.primitives.list.impl

Class ArrayLongList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joda.primitives.collection.impl.AbstractPrimitiveCollectable<Long>
      • org.joda.primitives.collection.impl.AbstractLongCollection
        • org.joda.primitives.list.impl.AbstractLongList
          • org.joda.primitives.list.impl.ArrayLongList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Iterable<Long>, Collection<Long>, List<Long>, LongCollection, PrimitiveCollection<Long>, LongIterable, LongList, PrimitiveList<Long>, PrimitiveCollectable<Long>

    public class ArrayLongList
extends AbstractLongList
implements Cloneable
    Array based implementation of LongList for primitive int elements.

    This class implements List allowing seamless integration with other APIs.

    Add, Remove, Set and Clear are supported.

    Since:
    1.0
